{"tid":444630,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"自問好鍾意識朋友嘅入","createTime":"2017-10-22T15:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T03:34:36.000Z","uid":141311,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"23ce87c66b5dbee38f131bd1c267d0157269b4f8","tid":444630,"uid":141311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲性格係會想識多啲出面多啲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識到但係總係覺得個感覺好唔實在 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畢竟佢唔係同你同學校/事... 變相唔會有common fd 同埋好少一班班 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會有一定共同話題但係隔一陣又會dead 加單剔你等多幾日先再覆返你但係個話題已經唔再新鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自問對朋友好好 諗住真心fd咁去識每個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係次次都換嚟比人覺得理所當然嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋做好人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同慘過食屎 <br />\n好想識到真係志同道合嘅人同堅持返做個好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94895adfb3c731b402be06b40f0d982be020e1e9","tid":444630,"uid":141311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c25c9f4165ae4d9e503c849452878aac89af22","tid":444630,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:25:58.000Z","msg":"睇黎冇"},{"pid":"6fb707e2c40e23e52a6fe9b1e4186eac53295205","tid":444630,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:42:57.000Z","msg":"識咁多朋友做咩 深交幾個仲好"},{"pid":"79fed13b918e8fd22f8e885b9f6d7c919b6abd8e","tid":444630,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T17:59:40.000Z","msg":"講得好啱 如果冇common topic 真係冇野好傾 慢慢愈黎愈遠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果一齊有同一個興趣 會多野講好多<br />\n